---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="DD Sketch A | Takuya Asano"
  description="DD Sketch A by Takuya Asano, 浅野託矢. The first volume of a three-part return to the DD piano improvisation series, gathering DD12 to DD21."
  ogImage="https://asanotakuya.com/images/ddsketch_a.jpg"
  ogUrl="https://asanotakuya.com/works/dd-sketch-a"
  ogType="article"
>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-title">Takuya Asano</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/works">Works</a>
        <a href="/news">News</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="work-meta fade-in">2025 · Album</p>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in">DD Sketch A</h1>

      <p class="fade-in">
        The first volume in a three-part return to the DD series.
      </p>

      <div class="work-detail-image fade-in">
        <img src="/images/ddsketch_a.jpg" alt="DD Sketch A artwork" />
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 72px;">
        <p>
          <em>DD Sketch A</em> gathers DD12 to DD21 from the ongoing DD improvisation series.
        </p>

        <p>
          The first group of recordings, DD1 to DD11, had already been collected in the album <em>DD</em>.<br />
          The works that followed continued to unfold over time, shaped quietly alongside other releases such as <em>Cinnamon</em> and <em>Cucumber</em>.
        </p>

        <p>
          With <em>DD Sketch</em>, these earlier recordings are returned to as a three-part sequence: A, B, and C.
        </p>

        <p>
          This first volume opens that sequence like the first pages of a sketchbook — a set of small studies gathered into a renewed flow.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 56px;">
        <p>
          The first volume of <em>DD Sketch</em>, gathering DD12 to DD21 into a renewed sequence.<br />
          Released in 2025.
        </p>

        <p lang="ja">
          DDシリーズのうち、DD12からDD21を収めた作品集。<br />
          過去の録音をあらためて束ね直し、3部作の最初の巻として再構成しています。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 72px;">
        <a
          href="https://open.spotify.com/intl-ja/album/0v6OAiXlyVD8U7FXBjxm5K?si=DTHG8G8xRO-1VpV1pqseCg"
          class="text-link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Listen
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="fade-in" style="margin-top: 80px;">
        <a href="/works" class="text-link">Back to Works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".fade-in").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  </script>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <nav class="footer-secondary">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/takuya_asano_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@TakuyaAsanoDD" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a>
        <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/2EXtaUmvzUTnfXZx14NoDx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Spotify</a>
        <a href="https://music.apple.com/jp/artist/%E6%B5%85%E9%87%8E%E8%A8%97%E7%9F%A2/1659347974" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple Music</a>
        <a href="https://takuyaasano.bandcamp.com/music" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bandcamp</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="footer-copy">© Takuya Asano / 浅野託矢</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
